WEBVTT

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:30.830
on the road, a man suddenly touched me.

00:01:31.190 --> 00:01:32.960
I was shocked.

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:36.810
By the time I realized it was wrong, 
the man had run away.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:39.660
