00:01:39.950 --> 00:01:42.190
Maybe there were no words 
to understand this;

00:01:42.190 --> 00:01:44.790
just a sense of violation, 
which is there even today.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:47.320
I changed the way I walked.

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.960
Elbows out, school bag in front,
fists clenched, angry eyes,

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:54.500
